    "title": "Job Opening Teacher at FIITJEE",
    "description": "Join the FIITJEE family as a Teacher in Kochi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout FIITJEE:\nFIITJEE is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FIITJEE!",
